lead_paragraph: Adam Scott survived a nightmare 15th hole to move one step closer to a 12th PGA Tour victory as he ended the third round of the Honda Classic in a tie for the lead with Sergio Garcia at Palm Beach Gardens in Florida on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Scott and Garcia Share Honda Classic Lead
headline.main: Scott and Garcia Share Honda Classic Lead
